lead_paragraph: Australia's new-look side delivered the minimum required with a victory over South Africa in the dead rubber third test on Sunday but there was understandable caution about proclaiming it the dawning of a new era Down Under.

headline.print_headline: Questions Remain Despite Australia's Victory in Adelaide
